OL,3,C'Don't turn your back on us': Farmers
OL,4,CUnion message to government
OL,6,FThe National Farmers Union (NFU) is
OL,7,Furging the Government not to "turn
OL,8,Fyour back on farmers" ahead of the
OL,9,Fautumn budget.
OL,11,FFarmers are demanding clarity from the
OL,12,FGovernment warning their businesses
OL,13,Fare at a tipping point - with climate
OL,14,Fchange and Brexit causing huge
OL,15,Fchallenges.
OL,17,FThe budget on Wednesday, 30 October,
OL,18,Fis likely to see cuts across
OL,19,Fgovernment departments, meaning the
OL,20,Ffarming budgets could be scaled back.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
