OL,3,C'Don't turn your back on us': Farmers
OL,4,CUnion message to government
OL,6,FJon Forshaw has been growing
OL,7,Fvegetables and potatoes on his farm
OL,8,Fnear Preston for 30 years and says
OL,9,Fthere has been a lot of change in the
OL,10,Ffarming industry of the past decade.
OL,12,FJon, a member of the NFU, says the
OL,13,FGovernment needs to to focus on the
OL,14,Fsupport farmers receive and the
OL,15,Findustry "even more".
OL,17,F"Food in general isn't really valued
OL,18,Fanymore and I think they need to start
OL,19,Flooking at it even more," he said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
