OL,3,C'Don't turn your back on us': Farmers
OL,4,CUnion message to government
OL,6,F"A guy once said to me, 'you need a
OL,7,Ffarmed three times a day and you need
OL,8,Fto eat'.
OL,10,F"We've always been there and they
OL,11,Falways kind of think we always will be
OL,12,Fthere. I think it's quite narrow-
OL,13,Fminded."
OL,15,FFrom Brexit, the energy crisis,
OL,16,Finflation and climate change, the
OL,17,Fregion's farmers say they have
OL,18,Fweathered many challenges.
