OL,3,C'Don't turn your back on us': Farmers
OL,4,CUnion message to government
OL,6,FIt is thought to be one of the reasons
OL,7,Fwhy the Conservative vote was slashed
OL,8,Fin rural North West seats.
OL,10,FHowever, John fears that even though
OL,11,Fthere is a new Government, old issues
OL,12,Fmight resurface unless there is
OL,13,Fstability and investment to make the
OL,14,Findustry more self-sufficient.
OL,16,F"The cost could triple overnight", he
OL,17,Fsaid. "You look at fertiliser and it's
OL,18,Fincreased from #300 or #400 a tonne to
OL,19,F#1000 a tonne.
