OL,3,C'Don't turn your back on us': Farmers
OL,4,CUnion message to government
OL,6,F"You can't go back to the supermarket
OL,7,Fand say you suddenly want three times
OL,8,Fthe amount.
OL,10,F"It comes to the point where you can't
OL,11,Fkeep risking large amounts of money to
OL,12,Feither flooding or global volatility.
OL,13,FIt's too expensive to grow a crop for
OL,14,Fnothing."
OL,16,FThe NFU says that #5.6billion is
OL,17,Fneeded so UK farms can meet their
OL,18,Ftargets and protect the environment,
OL,19,Fdeliver food security and boost
OL,20,Feconomic growth.
