OL,3,C'Don't turn your back on us': Farmers
OL,4,CUnion message to government
OL,6,F"We have 70 million people living on
OL,7,Fan island here and we need a plan for
OL,8,Fhow we're going to feed those 70
OL,9,Fmillion people and that requires
OL,10,Finvestment from the Government.
OL,12,F"Our members need the confidence to
OL,13,Finvest in their businesses so they can
OL,14,Fdeliver for economic growth and for
OL,15,Ffood security."
OL,17,FTom thinks that at the moment "we are
OL,18,Fat a pivotal time" where the
OL,19,Fgovernment can build confidence and
OL,20,Fsay to farmers 'we are with you' or
OL,21,F"they can walk away from us".
